<p><br /></p>

<blockquote>
  <p>Ligand recognition</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Isothermal titration calorimetry studies of the native <i>czcD</i> riboswitches show no response to Mn<sup>II</sup>, a weak response to Zn<sup>II</sup>, and similar dissociation constants (‚àº1ŒºM) and conformational responses for Fe<sup>II</sup>, Co<sup>II</sup>, and Ni<sup>II</sup><sup>[4]</sup>.</p>
<table class="table table-bordered" style="table-layout:fixed;width:1000px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto;">
<tr>
<td style="text-align:center;padding-bottom: 0px;padding-left: 0px;padding-top: 0px;padding-right: 0px">
  <img src="/images/ligand_recognition/NiCo_riboswitch_ligand_recognition.svg" alt="drawing" style="width:1000px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;" />
</td>
</tr>
